4 Quick Start
*************

4.1 Basic Usage
===============

  1. Launch Ollama Buddy:
          M-x ollama-buddy-menu
     or use your configured keybinding (e.g., ‚ÄòC-c o‚Äô).

  2. The menu will show available options.  Press the corresponding key
     for the action you want.

  3. To open the chat interface, press ‚Äòo‚Äô or select "Open Chat".

  4. In the chat buffer, type your prompt and press ‚ÄòC-c C-c‚Äô to send
     it.

  5. The AI will respond in the chat buffer.

4.2 Common Operations
=====================

Sending text from a file
