     Message" (or press ‚Äòg‚Äô).

Changing models
     Press ‚ÄòC-c m‚Äô to switch between available models, or ‚ÄòC-u C-c m‚Äô to
     select from cloud models.

Using the transient menu
     Press ‚ÄòC-c O‚Äô for the main transient menu with all features
     organized by category.

Attaching files
     Press ‚ÄòC-c C-a‚Äô to attach a file, or use the transient menu
     "Attachments" section.

Toggling reasoning visibility
     Press ‚ÄòC-c V‚Äô to hide or show reasoning/thinking sections in
     responses.

Using Awesome ChatGPT Prompts
     Select text, press ‚ÄòC-c o‚Äô, then ‚Äòa‚Äô for the Awesome prompts menu,
