14.1 Understanding Roles
========================

Roles in Ollama Buddy are collections of commands with specific
configurations:
   ‚Ä¢ Each role has its own set of commands
   ‚Ä¢ Commands can use specific models
   ‚Ä¢ Commands can have specialized system prompts
   ‚Ä¢ Commands can have specialized parameters

   This allows you to create specialized assistants for different
