     ollama-buddy-role-creator-create-new-role‚Äô
  2. Enter a name for your role (e.g., "programmer")
  3. Enter the number of menu columns (default: 2)
  4. For each command you want to add:
        ‚Ä¢ Specify a command name (e.g., "refactor-code")
        ‚Ä¢ Choose a key shortcut for the menu
        ‚Ä¢ Add a description
        ‚Ä¢ Optionally specify a model
        ‚Ä¢ Optionally add prompt prefixes and system messages

